		"description":{
			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>This glittering sphere stores psionic energy that you can unleash when your own power has waned.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Implement</b><b>:</b> Orb</p>\n<p class=\"basics\"><b>Enhancement Bonus:</b> Attack Rolls and Damage Rolls</p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Critical:</b> +3d6 critical damage</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power ✦ Daily (Free Action)</b></p><p>Expend 1 or 2 power points and place them in the orb. They remain there until you use them or until you take an extended rest.</p><p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power ✦ Daily (Free Action)</b></p><p>Requirement: You must have at least 1 power point stored inside the orb.</p><p><i>Trigger:</i> You make an attack using an unaugmented attack power.</p><p><i>Effect:</i> You can augment the triggering power by spending 1 power point from the orb, instead of using your own power points to augment the power.</p><p>Level 25 or 30: You can augment the triggering attack by spending 1 or 2 power points from the orb.</p>",
